Usage: write_ml_library [-help] [-objects <object_list>] -prefix <string>

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-objects <object_list>     # List of library object(s) to dump, one or more of
                           # { lib_arc lib_cell lib_pin library library_set
                           # power_table timing_table } (tcl_obj, optional)
-prefix <string>           # Prefix for output files (string, required)